{"title":"诗二首","authors":["刘冈英"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":4,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗二首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘冈英　遗作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤大地是我的母亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"特殊的偏爱啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长久的深埋底层，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出头露面只是为了献身"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——生命的最后旅程。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫埋怨筛孔的直径，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快认真粉碎了自己。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史在公正的旋转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不拒绝合格的颗粒。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}